text: Thomas Cuisset (March 19, 1958 – January 19, 2017) was a French photographer. He was a resident artist at the Villa Medici in 1992. He won the Prix Moins Trente in 1987, and the Prix de photographie from the Académie des Beaux-Arts in 2009. ==References== Category:1958 births Category:2017 deaths Category:People from Maubeuge Category:People from Montreuil, Seine-Saint- Denis Category:French photographers Category:Deaths from cancer in France
